This directory contains the source code distribution
of the UMLErl -- UML statemachines in Erlang -- tool.

For instructions on how to install UMLErl and use it to simulate
and verify a small example see http://babel.ls.fi.upm.es/~fred/umerl/.

For Licence conditions see the file LICENCE.

The directory examples contains a number of examples (a variant
of the Dining Philosopher problem, a locker, etc) suitable
for running under UMLErl.

For questions or to submit comments regarding the tool please send an email
to lfredlund@fi.upm.es
